Description:
Extravagant Docklands living at The Quays with breathtaking water views to compliment
When it comes to breathtaking water views, this elegantly appointed and immaculately presented One-bedroom with One-car space apartment needs to be on your "Must See" list if visiting Docklands precinct.
A rare and exciting opportunity exists to purchase in the highly sought after, exclusive apartment complex, "The Quays".
Offering first class accommodation, the property maximises its outlook, a modern open floor plan incorporates generous living/dining zone and where huge glass aspects facilitate amazing natural light, leading to a spacious balcony overlooking the incredible water views. The elegant marble kitchen with European appliances is all ready for 5-star cooking. This spacious bright bedroom also comes with built-in-robe.
Additional features include security access, reverse cycle air-conditioning and secure car parking.
This sensational "The Quays" complex offers a Health Club with a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio, while there is a Resident's Club on level one with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room and cinema lounge. Further enjoy a rooftop garden with tennis court, BBQ and dining facilities.
Please contact Ary Tjin on 0423 891 891 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
?Docklands? Serrata,805-817 Bourke Street
This Serrata apartment is located in the heart of Victoria Harbor and situated on the 11th floor. It is in the close vicinity of local shops, fine restaurants, a supermarket and has easy access to open community spaces including parks, harbour and river promenade. Within the walking distance of Etihad Stadium, Waterfront City, Southern Cross Station and New Quay, this generous two-bedroom apartment offers a convenient city living.
The apartment is also energy-efficient and comes with secure intercom and heating.
A bright and spacious living zone opens out to the large terrace, while the excellently tiled kitchen has a well-crafted stone benchtop and impressive steel appliances. A large bedroom featuring sliding door access from the living zone allows flexibility when it comes to open or private living, while the elegant bathroom further boasts a concealed laundry.

Description:
VIEWS AS FAR AS THE EYE CAN SEE
Being almost on the top floor, you are overlooking rooftops of pretty much most of Melbourne CBD, Marvel Stadium where you can watch the screens of the concerts and sports games from your own living room in perfect peace! Spectacular views day or night as far as Mornington Peninsula!
We are finding it hard to find anything disappointing about this beautiful apartment. Guaranteed not to hang around for long, we strongly recommended inspecting on a private basis at your earliest convenience.
- Balcony views over the harbour, city and as far out to the peninsula!
- 22nd floor immaculate developed by MAB
- Hardwood flooring throughout
- Floor to ceiling glass across lounge & kitchen
- 3 double bedrooms with fitted wardrobes and Master walk in robe
- 3 bathrooms and ensuites
- Upgraded Miele kitchen with integrated appliances
The sensational Quays complex offers a Health Club with a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio, while there is a Resident's Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. Further enjoy a rooftop garden with tennis court, BBQ and dining facilities.
The NewQuay precinct is a lively hub and home to some of the Docklands best attractions. Trams will take you over all over Melbourne including the MCG, Richmond, Hawthorn, and Box Hill, while surrounding restaurants cover cuisines of all types. You're also moments to Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Medibank Icehouse, Costco, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, and the iconic Festival Hall.
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235
Internal area
127m²

Description:
Brilliant Views in a sought after building
Overlooking Victoria Harbour with uninterrupted views towards the Yarra River this brilliant two bedroom apartment is sure to appeal to discerning buyers looking for something out of the ordinary. Located in the heart of the Docklands this apartment is only moments away from Cafes, Restaurants, harbour town and marvel stadium.
With a generous floor plan and well separated spaces this designer apartment has everything the inner city dweller could need. With sizeable bedrooms, master with en suite, walk through wardrobe and private balcony. The second bedroom also has its own private balcony and built in wardrobes. This along with a second bathroom and European laundry make this apartment a standout.
The best part of this apartment is sure to be the free flowing kitchen, dining and living area adjoined to your third and largest balcony with views from every angle overlooking the harbour. This apartment surely has everything including, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a health club with rooftop pool, gym, and private function area.
Others close by attractions include Harbour Town shopping mall, Costco supermarket, bike paths, Trams only minutes away, CBD only 5 - 10 minutes stroll, Southern Cross station and parklands.

Description:
Affordable two bedroom with fantastic light and city views
Boasting a number of fantastic highlights from an appealing northern orientation to wonderful natural light and dazzling CBD views, this smart and elegant two bedroom apartment is a Docklands delight in the NewQuay precinct.
Situated in the North Tower of the exclusive The Quays complex
Formal entry hall leads directly into the stone-featured kitchen which comes with timber floors, elegant dark cabinetry, stainless steel appliances and space for casual meals
Light-filled and north-facing carpeted lounge is the perfect space for everyday living
Lounge opens out to the relaxed balcony which has picturesque views of the city to the east and mountain ranges to the north
Two bedrooms includes the main bedroom with mirrored BIR and access to balcony
Stylish bathroom
European laundry
Split system heating and cooling
Secure intercom entry
Secure car space
AMENITIES
The Quays features a Health Club with a pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, Residents Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge, and a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.

Sweeping Harbour and City Views in the Lap of Luxury!
Brilliantly boasting a spectacular Victoria Harbour and city skyline outlook, this dramatically daring 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment is designed for easy living and memorable entertaining. Immerse yourself in a wonderful sense of sunlit space and the ultimate in waterfront style so close to Woolworths shopping and New Quay restaurants with the free tram on your doorstep connecting you with the entire city.
Superbly set on the 27th floor, discover wide-reaching open-plan living and dining with an oversized picture window expertly framing the harbour. Be instantly drawn to an undercover balcony and entertain in numbers day and night overlooking Victoria Harbour and engaging in breathtaking views of Marvel Stadium with the stunning city rising from behind. Both mirror-robed bedrooms are generous in size and filled with light, serviced by a fully tiled bathroom and ensuite with mirrored cabinetry and rain-shower fittings.
Take advantage of a concealed laundry, secure parking, split-system heating/cooling in the living area and main bedroom, double glazing, roller blinds over openable windows, recessed down-lighting, and secure intercom entry. Enjoy exclusive access to resort-style facilities including a residents lounge/library, indoor lap pool, spa, state-of- the-art gym, and a BBQ garden terrace. Move straight in and apply your personal touch today!

Description:
Vogue Living @ The Mariner
Perched and hovering high on the 7th floor, cosy corner unit, of the beautiful "The Mariner" development. This north facing - perfectly situated apartment is overlooking at the magnificent water front view and would make a fantastic investment property investment with plenty of opportunity. Stunning, contemporary, this exquisite 1-bedroom apartment is completed with 1- bathroom, flawless layout, natural light flowing throughout that exudes style.
Featuring open plan living/dining area, opening out to private balcony, reverse cycle air-conditioning and built in robes. The well thought out stylish kitchen includes European appliances, gas cooktop, dishwasher, sleek timber cabinetry with separate pantry.
With plenty of on street parking at nearby Barassi Park, bike storage, public transport, Harbour Town shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and Citylink. The location is just fantastic.
Please contact Ary Tjin on 0423 891 891 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Family-Sized Arkley Entertainer in Prime Podium Position
A compelling combination of supersized sunlit space, impeccable finishes, and a stunning Victoria Harbour aspect, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment creates a style as timeless as the spectacular water views. The celebrated luxury lifestyle on the podium level of Arkley tower is further enhanced downstairs within walking distance of free city trams, Marvel Stadium, popular Newquay restaurants, The District shopping, and even the CBD itself.
The free-flowing floorplan uses space thoughtfully with an inviting entrance hallway leading to spacious living/dining, and a granite-topped, high-end kitchen complete with a welcoming breakfast bar and stainless-steel Smeg and Bosch appliances. Floor-to-ceiling glass directs natural light to every far-reaching corner, opening up to an oversized balcony with relaxed views over Victoria Harbour. Well appointed, all 3 robed bedrooms are roomy with the palatial main featuring a deluxe ensuite, while a family-sized bathroom boasts a luxurious bath. Enjoy 2 secure car spaces and a pair of extra-large storage cages, all ideally located on the same level as the apartment.
Designed and constructed with a superior commitment to quality, special features include a full-sized laundry, intercom entry, split-system heating and cooling, and first-class resort-style facilities with exclusive access to a pool, spa, fully fitted gym, and a golf practice net. A smart choice for a growing family, a wise investment, or downsizing in unrivalled style, this one will not last long!
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
Podium perfection with uninterrupted harbour vistas
Positioned on the podium level of the standout Arkley complex which only has 24 apartments in this boutique section of the building, this bright and elegant 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom retreat offers breathtaking harbour views and genuine modern appeal.
Features 99 sqm (approx.) of fantastic internal space!
Make the most of a secure car space and a storage room on the same floor
Striking timber floors splashed throughout the light-filled lounge and meals zone which have floor-to-ceiling windows which frame the memorable Victoria Harbour views
Undercover balcony the prime place to take in the water views as well as Marvel Stadium and the city to the east and sunsets to the west
Stone kitchen includes a long island bench and stainless steel Smeg and Bosch appliances
Master bedroom boasts its own south-facing balcony with water views as well as a walk-in robe and stylish ensuite
2nd bedroom with built-in robe storage
Bathroom is immaculately presented and comes with a separate powder room
Separate laundry room
Ducted heating and cooling plus additional reverse cycle cooling
Secure video intercom
Named after one of Australias most famous artists Howard Arkley, this complex offers residents access to a swimming pool, spa, golf practice net, and gym.
The fantastic NewQuay precinct is close to so many great waterside restaurants including Renzos, Cocobei, Fish Bar, and Berth Restaurant just to name a few. Youre also close to District Docklands with Hoyts Cinemas, 8 Street hawker food outlets, Woolworths supermarket, Dan Murphys, and the Market Lane fresh food precinct with butchers, delis, bakeries, and coffee roasters, Marvel Stadium, an abundance of CBD attractions, Capital City Trail, nearby trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and the airport Skybus.
Internal area
107m²

Sub-penthouse stunner with exceptional views and amazing space
With stunning views from all rooms, an incredible amount of internal space, and enviable modern luxury, this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom sub-penthouse apartment is out of this world!
On the private and peaceful 28th floor with only two other apartments on the level
Enjoy 176 sqm (approx.) of internal space
Views include Port Phillip Bay, Yarra River, mountain ranges to the north, and the iconic CBD
Expansive lounge and dining enjoys brilliant light and the superb views through full windows
Stone kitchen has integrated fridge and freezer plus full Miele appliances including a coffee machine
Master bedroom boasts entry out to the dual access balcony along with city views, mirrored BIRs, and luxurious double vanity ensuite
Other bedrooms showcase bays views (incl. 1 bedrm with foldaway bed)
Stylish bathroom and a separate powder room with European laundry
Ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry
Brand new carpet
3 secure car spaces with overhead storage area

Description:
EXCLUSIVE YARRAS EDGE
This apartment is perfect for owner-occupiers and CBD professionals who will love its easy care nature and great riverside location. The apartment has a generous lounge and dining opens which opens out to a large balcony, which is a great outdoor space that can be used all year long thanks to its privacy and inspired views of the marina below.
The standout modern style combines with a thoughtful open layout and low-maintenance feel to produce this sensational north-facing two bedroom apartment, which is located in the highly sought-after Yarra's Edge precinct.
It's well-appointed kitchen delivers a sleekly tiled splashback, stone surfaces, island bench, and stainless steel appliances, meanwhile both bedrooms have mirrored built-in robes including the ultra-spacious main bedroom. The 2nd bedroom also has direct balcony access. Other highlights include a bathroom with European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, video intercom, secure car space on the same floor for easy access.
You have the short walk to South Wharf attractions including DFO shopping and restaurants and bars including Bangpop, Munich Brauhaus, The General Assembly, Plus 5 Bar, Meat Market, and The Boatbuilders Yard just to name a few. You're also close to Crown Casino with world class restaurants, CBD, and transport including Southern Cross Station and trams on Spencer Street.
You will also have access to a wonderful roof top facility along with the access to the RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
To inspect please call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235.

90m²
